# Cloudflare Turnstile SITE key for the contact form widget.
# Without it, the form falls back to Cloudflare's test key, which shows a
# "For testing only" banner. Set the real value here for local dev (copy this
# file to `.env`), and in Cloudflare Pages → build environment variables for prod.
# Note: the SITE key is public by design (visible in the page HTML) — only the
# Turnstile SECRET key must stay private (it lives as a Worker secret).
PUBLIC_TURNSTILE_SITE_KEY=
